snippet.title: GameGuru Intro Video 2018
snippet.description:
Available on Steam here; http://store.steampowered.com/app/266310/GameGuru/
With GameGuru creating, sharing and selling your own games has never been easier! Sculpt your virtual 3D world, drop in trees, buildings, characters, and other game elements - then press a button & your game is made!
